<div id="conservation" class="fl-module fl-module-heading fl-node-rpytgfq4mlkz" data-node="rpytgfq4mlkz">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<h2 class="fl-heading">
		<span class="fl-heading-text">CONSERVATION / TOURISM</span>
	</h2>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-kib9rmw3658q" data-node="kib9rmw3658q">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p><strong>2014 - <a title="HB1116 - opens in a new window" href="http://lis.virginia.gov/cgi-bin/legp604.exe?141+sum+HB1116" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HB1116</a> - Banister River; Scenic River designation.</strong></p>
<p>Extends the State Scenic River designation of the Banister River from the current 38.4 miles to 63.3 miles. - <a title="HB1116 - opens in a new window" href="http://lis.virginia.gov/cgi-bin/legp604.exe?141+sum+HB1116" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read More</a></p>
